Well, that was awkward.

16:10.767 --> 16:13.898
Baby, it's just an old lady
Making an honest mistake.

16:13.900 --> 16:16.432
Yeah, she thought tasha was
The first lady.

16:17.634 --> 16:19.332
Look, you think you
Have time later.

16:19.334 --> 16:21.732
To look at a budget for
The streaming setup?

