Zora up from counseling.

16:24.000 --> 16:26.132
Maybe tonight We can look at it.

16:26.134 --> 16:28.699
- Alright, I'll print 'em out.
- Okay.

16:28.701 --> 16:30.165
- You do your thing.
- Okay.

16:34.300 --> 16:36.598
I have made sacrifices, Kevin,

16:36.600 --> 16:39.398
Both during our relationship
And after.

16:39.400 --> 16:40.465
Is that a lie?

16:40.467 --> 16:42.398
No, it's not a lie, Charity.

16:42.400 --> 16:45.398
Doing this tour
Is a dream for me.

16:45.400 --> 16:46.898
I'm going back
Wednesday morning.

16:46.900 --> 16:48.532
Okay, And I want you to go,

16:48.534 --> 16:50.565
But you're gonna leave
Nathan with me.

16:50.567 --> 16:52.298
Why are you doing This to me?

16:52.300 --> 16:53.598
