Complete strangers, isn't he?

17:00.934 --> 17:02.665
Kevin, you have a job, Too.

17:02.667 --> 17:05.265
It's not like childcare
Is a bad thing.

17:05.267 --> 17:06.732
It's a part of life.

17:06.733 --> 17:10.598
Look, all I'm saying is, it
Is difficult for an adult.

17:10.599 --> 17:12.998
On the road let
Alone a small child.

17:13.000 --> 17:16.132
Why drag him Around like that?

17:16.134 --> 17:19.931
Does that sound like
Good parenting to you?

17:19.933 --> 17:22.731
Charity, I'm his father.

17:22.733 --> 17:26.131
Leave him with me.

17:26.133 --> 17:27.464
He'll be okay.

17:30.334 --> 17:33.665
Pastor, here is
The payroll report.

17:34.867 --> 17:36.632
Thank you.

17:38.467 --> 17:41.132
Wow, tasha, I don't know
What we'd do without you.

17:41.134 --> 17:42.598
