- Seriously.

17:42.600 --> 17:45.065
No, do you know how many
Pastors in your position...

17:45.067 --> 17:47.532
Hey, forget pastors, first
Lady's would've kicked me.

17:47.534 --> 17:49.065
To the curb When they took over?

17:53.933 --> 17:56.398
Are you contemplating
A life change?

17:56.400 --> 17:59.431
No, just shopping For kerissa.

17:59.433 --> 18:00.765
Yeah, she's been so busy Lately,

18:00.767 --> 18:02.365
I just wanted to do
Something nice for her.

18:02.367 --> 18:06.065
Aw, sweet, well, what
About some jewelry.

18:06.067 --> 18:07.998
Because you know,
Clothes, we always end up.

18:08.000 --> 18:10.798
Taking that stuff Back anyway.

18:10.800 --> 18:12.665
Can you find good
Jewelry online?

18:12.667 --> 18:15.331
On... lord have mercy,
You cannot find jewelry.

18:15.333 --> 18:16.465
On the internet.

18:16.467 --> 18:18.732
You need to look at it,
Lay it out,

18:18.734 --> 18:21.698
Touch all the surfaces
Of the stones.

18:21.700 --> 18:23.698
I can take you To my shop.

18:23.700 --> 18:25.065
Really? It's kind of late.

18:25.067 --> 18:27.365
You sure you have time?
Time to look at jewelry?

18:27.367 --> 18:29.432
Do you know who you're
Talking to right now?

18:31.067 --> 18:32.865
Plus, I could really go
For a glass of champagne.

18:32.867 --> 18:34.198
