18:34.200 --> 18:38.732
Yeah, that's how
My jeweler gets down, okay?

18:38.734 --> 18:41.499
Okay. I got to see this place.

18:42.867 --> 18:44.332
Mae Clara,
Is everything alright?

18:44.334 --> 18:46.665
The food is lovely.

18:46.667 --> 18:48.998
If cornbread could sing,
You would have heard.

18:49.000 --> 18:51.998
The hallelujah chorus
Coming out in the oven.

18:52.867 --> 18:54.699
