19:17.301 --> 19:19.232
It's the paintings.

19:19.234 --> 19:20.831
You've changed The paintings.

19:20.833 --> 19:22.765
Lord.

19:22.767 --> 19:25.665
The mclean castillos.

19:25.667 --> 19:26.665
Yes.

19:26.667 --> 19:28.998
Yes, yes, yes.

19:29.000 --> 19:31.431
Just felt like it
Was time to move on.

19:32.700 --> 19:35.231
Horace would get so upset
With me.

19:35.233 --> 19:37.098
When I moved things around.

19:37.100 --> 19:38.932
