19:41.534 --> 19:43.132
You know, he does, too.

19:43.134 --> 19:45.598
Been missing him hard Lately.

19:45.600 --> 19:49.065
Well, we miss the two
Of you together, too.

19:49.067 --> 19:51.232
- Yes.
- Still so much in love.

19:51.234 --> 19:54.765
Just like me and mae,
After all those years.

19:54.767 --> 19:56.565
How long has it
Been for you two?

19:56.567 --> 20:00.031
- 44 years.
- Soon to be 45.

20:00.033 --> 20:01.099
45.

20:02.567 --> 20:03.665
Y'all going on a trip?

20:06.267 --> 20:08.932
I hope I didn't Ruin a surprise.

20:08.934 --> 20:11.265
No, no, no.

20:13.067 --> 20:15.165
You haven't Ruined anything.

20:18.134 --> 20:19.565
Clara, are you alright?

20:20.901 --> 20:23.399
Just thinking Of horace.

20:26.567 --> 20:29.865
You two are so blessed.

20:29.867 --> 20:33.465
And we never forget it,
Do we, dear?

20:33.467 --> 20:34.467
Never.

20:36.000 --> 20:37.932
They're all really nice.

20:37.934 --> 20:39.732
What about this one?

20:43.400 --> 20:45.565
What's gonna get?

20:45.567 --> 20:47.765
You don't like it?

20:47.767 --> 20:50.498
It's nice, but that
Necklace is more like,

20:50.500 --> 20:55.132
"I like you a lot,"
Whereas this one...

20:55.134 --> 20:58.265
Now, this says,
"You are my world."

20:58.267 --> 21:02.465
This is from
A new young designer.

21:02.467 --> 21:05.332
Come on now.

21:05.334 --> 21:06.798
This is beautiful.

21:06.800 --> 21:09.299
It would look even more
Beautiful against your skin.

21:09.301 --> 21:10.399
- May I?
- May you?

21:10.401 --> 21:14.398
If you... hurry up and
Get that on me.

21:14.400 --> 21:16.065
My goodness.

21:22.867 --> 21:23.998
Well?

21:24.000 --> 21:25.798
When you're right, You're right.

21:25.800 --> 21:27.632
I got to look at this.

21:31.267 --> 21:33.965
My god.

21:33.967 --> 21:37.632
This is the most beautiful thing
I've ever seen.

21:37.634 --> 21:39.698
It's so gorgeous, I can't
Even breathe right now.

21:39.700 --> 21:40.765
Wow.

21:40.767 --> 21:42.998
I'm sure basie
Bought you nice things.

21:43.000 --> 21:45.998
I mean, sure, he got me
Things, but then it would.

21:46.000 --> 21:47.998
Be, like, a day or two later
And he'd say, "Baby, honey",

21:48.000 --> 21:52.132
"I got into this gambling
Situation" and, you know.

21:52.134 --> 21:54.332
I'm sorry you
Had to deal with that.

21:55.800 --> 21:57.565
Well, you'd never
Do that to kerissa.

21:58.767 --> 21:59.767
Wow.

22:04.167 --> 22:05.365
Um...

22:05.367 --> 22:08.198
I'll take it.

22:08.200 --> 22:09.931
Great.

22:09.933 --> 22:12.898
Well, just hold On a hot minute.

22:12.900 --> 22:15.532
I need to lock this
In my memory bank now.

22:17.100 --> 22:19.865
