22:19.867 --> 22:21.665
Charity And you'll love this.

22:21.667 --> 22:25.332
He's an expert In parenting now.

22:25.334 --> 22:26.565
Telling me that

22:26.567 --> 22:29.831
I shouldn't take nathan
On the road with me.

22:29.833 --> 22:31.098
Well, it is Just six weeks.

22:31.100 --> 22:34.231
Exactly, I wouldn't be
Taking him if it was.

22:34.233 --> 22:37.498
For six months, Would I?

22:37.500 --> 22:41.099
No, so go ahead, kevin,
Take me to court.

22:41.101 --> 22:43.132
Well, he just might.

22:43.134 --> 22:44.532
I don't care.

22:45.867 --> 22:48.398
It's like I'd be rewarding
Him for being a jerk.

22:48.400 --> 22:51.265
Look, I know you're angry,
But you did say.

22:51.267 --> 22:53.265
That kevin Was a good father.

22:53.267 --> 22:56.499
Hey, sweetie. What's up, peanut?

22:57.401 --> 22:59.198
What you doing here?

22:59.200 --> 23:01.665
Tagged along with sophia,

23:01.667 --> 23:04.732
Trying to get Some "K" time.

23:04.734 --> 23:05.865
Sister wisdom.

23:08.134 --> 23:10.399
- Where you been?
- Out running an errand.

23:10.401 --> 23:11.599
What errand?

23:11.601 --> 23:14.065
I'll tell you later.

23:14.067 --> 23:15.998
Where's zora?

23:16.000 --> 23:18.398
She's in her room With sophia.

23:18.400 --> 23:20.465
Okay.

23:20.467 --> 23:21.532
You been drinking?

23:21.534 --> 23:23.065
Sure asking A lot of questions.

23:27.000 --> 23:28.899
Don't give up on a dream
Out of spite.

23:33.867 --> 23:35.532
That is so thirsty.

23:35.534 --> 23:38.332
- For real.
- My god.

23:38.334 --> 23:39.334
My god.

23:43.834 --> 23:45.765
Thanks for coming over.

23:45.767 --> 23:48.732
Thanks for the invite.
I thought you were mad at me.

23:48.734 --> 23:52.132
I was, but I'm over it.

23:52.134 --> 23:54.332
Good.

23:54.334 --> 23:56.532
Can you do me A favor, though?

23:56.534 --> 23:57.599
Sure, what do you need?

23:58.801 --> 24:00.798
Like, one of those
Pre-paid phones.

24:00.800 --> 24:02.199
From wal-mart Or something.

24:03.867 --> 24:05.798
Are you sure That's a good idea?

24:05.800 --> 24:09.132
Sophia, I'm going
Crazy in this room.

24:09.134 --> 24:10.598
I can't use my phone,

24:10.600 --> 24:12.798
I can't watch tv,
Use the internet.

24:12.800 --> 24:16.565
I had to use the warden's
Phone just to call you.

24:17.867 --> 24:20.598
Please, if I cannot communicate
With the outside world,

24:20.600 --> 24:25.332
I'm going to lose my
Entire mind, please?

24:25.334 --> 24:27.799
You gonna call isaiah?

24:27.801 --> 24:30.132
- Sophia, come on.
- So you are.

24:30.134 --> 24:33.598
Then I can't do it.

24:33.600 --> 24:35.865
Can't or won't?

24:35.867 --> 24:38.398
He hits you, zora.

24:38.400 --> 24:42.132
He hits you and he
Treats you like crap.

24:42.134 --> 24:46.065
I won't. I'm sorry.

24:56.200 --> 24:58.031
Clara Look at the time.

24:58.033 --> 25:00.898
No, no, no, I've got
To get this old body home.

25:00.900 --> 25:06.265
Clara, there is a piece
Of business.

25:06.267 --> 25:08.865
That we wanted
To put on your heart.

25:08.867 --> 25:10.932
Church business?

25:10.934 --> 25:13.532
You know, Satan's always busy.

25:13.534 --> 25:14.998
That old devil
Sent us a tax bill,

25:15.000 --> 25:18.598
Saying we owe $2 million.

25:18.600 --> 25:21.732
- Another tax problem?
- The same one.

25:21.734 --> 25:25.198
Max said he would
Handle it, but he didn't.

25:25.200 --> 25:27.798
Well, you can't cuss him out,
Can you? He's dead now.

25:27.800 --> 25:29.332
They're saying we have
To pay what we owe.

25:29.334 --> 25:32.232
Plus interest And penalties.

25:32.234 --> 25:34.298
And james and I were
Hoping that you'd be able.

25:34.300 --> 25:37.165
To help us out here.

25:37.167 --> 25:38.965
Is that why you asked me here?

25:38.967 --> 25:40.065
It's part of it, yes.

25:43.200 --> 25:44.732
Well, $2 million's a lot,

25:44.734 --> 25:46.965
Even for someone
With all my money.

25:46.967 --> 25:50.465
And we would never ask you
If it didn't mean everything.

25:50.467 --> 25:52.465
Please know that.

25:52.467 --> 25:53.998
You two don't have it?

25:54.000 --> 25:56.065
The past few years have
Been hard.

25:56.067 --> 25:57.765
For a variety Of reasons,

25:57.767 --> 25:59.365
We're not liquid right now.

25:59.367 --> 26:02.032
I... We could probably
Pay, I don't know,

26:02.034 --> 26:04.865
A couple of hundred
Thousand, but that's it.

26:04.867 --> 26:09.532
Look, if the answer Is no,

26:09.534 --> 26:12.998
Please know that
Our feelings for you.

26:13.000 --> 26:14.065
Won't change one bit.

26:14.067 --> 26:17.431
- No.
- But we need your help.

26:17.433 --> 26:18.865
The church Needs your help.

26:29.933 --> 26:33.398
You know, I'm gonna
Call rochelle later.

26:33.400 --> 26:34.798
You sure That's a good idea?

26:34.800 --> 26:36.665
To have her so involved
In the church?

26:36.667 --> 26:38.532
She's already involved.
Could you?

26:38.534 --> 26:39.798
Yeah.

26:39.800 --> 26:41.198
Not a day goes by
That she's not at the church.

26:41.200 --> 26:43.265
At least this way, I
Keep her in my sights.

26:43.267 --> 26:44.665
And out Of my father's office.

26:44.667 --> 26:47.198
Well, he's moved
Back in the house.

26:47.200 --> 26:50.132
Yeah, I don't know
What that's about.

26:50.134 --> 26:52.932
She's got him In the guest room.

26:52.934 --> 26:54.465
You can cut the tension
With a knife.

26:54.467 --> 26:57.965
I swear this is
So far from over.

26:57.967 --> 26:58.965
Does it ever occur To you.

26:58.967 --> 27:00.332
That maybe
Your father's the one?

27:00.334 --> 27:01.932
The one what?

27:01.934 --> 27:04.332
The one that's leading
This woman on?

27:04.334 --> 27:05.865
No, he wouldn't do that.

27:07.000 --> 27:08.999
Okay, it's just a thought,
Just a thought.

27:14.934 --> 27:17.065
Where are you going?

27:17.067 --> 27:18.998
I'm gonna go home.

27:19.000 --> 27:22.065
- Home?
- Yeah.

27:22.067 --> 27:23.931
My mother gave me An earful.

27:23.933 --> 27:26.265
About my sexual commerce
This morning.

27:26.267 --> 27:28.665
So going home Will prove what?

27:28.667 --> 27:30.732
Well, it'll get her
Off my back, for one.

27:30.734 --> 27:33.398
So you want her to think
We're not having sex?

27:33.400 --> 27:35.398
'Cause we just had sex.

27:35.400 --> 27:38.299
- I know.
- So stay.

27:40.734 --> 27:43.231
Don't be a hypocrite.

27:43.233 --> 27:46.632
Don't be just like her,
Don't be like all of them.

27:46.634 --> 27:48.065
Why do that?

27:53.034 --> 27:55.198
Thank you.

27:55.200 --> 27:56.532
For what?

28:01.967 --> 28:04.499
For making leaving Easier.

28:17.600 --> 28:18.600
What's going on?

28:20.067 --> 28:22.965
Sophia convinced us to
Let you have this back.

28:24.134 --> 28:26.399
She said We could trust you.

28:26.401 --> 28:29.399
She's a woman Of great insight.

28:31.267 --> 28:33.065
You're welcome.

28:33.067 --> 28:34.465
Thank you.

28:54.334 --> 28:57.199
We got it.

28:57.201 --> 28:58.665
She's gonna talk to
Her money manager.

28:58.667 --> 29:01.865
Nice work, first lady.

29:01.867 --> 29:04.165
What are we gonna
Do for our 45th?

29:04.167 --> 29:06.432
You know, A trip would be nice.

29:06.434 --> 29:09.632
It's got to be Something modest,

29:09.634 --> 29:11.265
But I guess togetherness
Is the point?

29:12.967 --> 29:15.965
What... What is it?

29:15.967 --> 29:17.832
What did you tell her?

29:17.834 --> 29:18.998
You heard every word.

29:19.000 --> 29:21.198
Not clara, rochelle.

29:21.200 --> 29:23.632
What do you mean telling her
About our family business?

29:23.634 --> 29:24.665
What did I tell rochelle?

29:24.667 --> 29:27.398
How does she know About zora?

29:29.467 --> 29:31.065
I...

29:31.067 --> 29:33.198
I guess I must have
Said something.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.200
When?

29:38.333 --> 29:40.065
Well, let me answer that.

29:40.067 --> 29:41.799
When the two of you
Were together at.

29:41.801 --> 29:43.932
The biltmore hotel.

29:43.934 --> 29:45.932
Is that who you were
With when you left?

29:45.934 --> 29:49.132
You went with her?
To go crying to her?!

29:50.701 --> 29:52.631
Do you not see that
You are willing this.

29:52.633 --> 29:54.565
Non-existent affair Into being?

29:54.567 --> 29:56.965
- I am not.
- Yes, you are.

29:56.967 --> 29:58.298
I mean, You're creating it.

29:58.300 --> 30:00.132
Only god creates From nothing.

30:00.134 --> 30:02.432
I'm just trying
To clean up your mess.

30:02.434 --> 30:05.165
Really?

30:05.167 --> 30:07.598
Well, What about your mess?

30:07.600 --> 30:10.765
You make such a show
Of all your strength, mae.

30:10.767 --> 30:12.932
But I swear, I've never
Seen a woman so fragile.

30:12.934 --> 30:17.032
That she cannot even
Consider her own sinfulness.

30:34.134 --> 30:36.798
Are you going to tell me?

30:36.800 --> 30:39.198
- Tell you what?
- Where you were.

30:39.200 --> 30:42.865
There you go With the questions.

30:42.867 --> 30:44.665
I was worried.

30:44.667 --> 30:46.798
Were you?

30:46.800 --> 30:48.665
Alright.

30:48.667 --> 30:51.198
I'm sorry.

30:51.200 --> 30:53.798
But look.

30:53.800 --> 30:55.998
I know how hard you work.

30:56.000 --> 30:58.798
For our family, for your
Students, for our church.

30:58.800 --> 31:01.132
No one works harder Than you.

31:03.067 --> 31:06.198
So I just wanted To say that.

31:06.200 --> 31:08.732
You are the first lady...

31:10.400 --> 31:13.998
And you're my first
Lady in every way.

31:14.000 --> 31:15.332
Is this where you were?

31:15.334 --> 31:16.532
Yes, it is.

31:17.734 --> 31:19.332
And it has champagne.

31:23.167 --> 31:25.432
It's beautiful, Jacob!

31:25.434 --> 31:27.065
Yeah? You like it?

31:27.067 --> 31:28.865
Good, I'm so glad You like it.

31:28.867 --> 31:29.865
Yeah, try it on.

31:29.867 --> 31:30.798
It's different!

31:30.800 --> 31:31.800
Yeah, very.

31:43.867 --> 31:44.899
There you go.

31:46.800 --> 31:48.665
Perfect.

31:48.667 --> 31:50.665
It's beautiful.

31:50.667 --> 31:52.698
Beauty on beauty.

31:52.700 --> 31:54.131
Thank you.

31:54.133 --> 31:57.332
You're welcome. Thank you.

32:05.067 --> 32:08.132
Meet me in the bedroom.

32:08.134 --> 32:09.532
Okay.

32:34.201 --> 32:35.465
Can I get you Anything, daddy?

32:35.467 --> 32:36.798
A refill? Something?

32:36.800 --> 32:39.265
No, no. I've had
Too much already.

32:49.800 --> 32:51.198
Mom was pretty upset.

32:51.200 --> 32:52.465
Don't you come After me.

32:52.467 --> 32:54.065
Not tonight,
Not you, not about this.

32:54.067 --> 32:55.932
She's up there Crying, daddy.

32:55.934 --> 32:58.731
Gigi, it's none
Of your business.

32:58.733 --> 33:00.398
It's my business when
I see rochelle cross.

33:00.400 --> 33:01.865
Parading in and out
Of your office.

33:01.867 --> 33:03.532
Like she owns The church.

33:03.534 --> 33:05.465
Mama is not wrong For wondering.

33:05.467 --> 33:08.398
There's nothing between
Me and ms. Cross!

33:08.400 --> 33:09.932
Then let her go.

33:11.667 --> 33:13.065
